                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>052900</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <div type="textpart" n="a">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Φιλωνίδης"><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Φιλ</supplied>ωνί<subst><del rend="corrected">ι</del><add place="overstrike">δ</add></subst>ης</name></persName>
                        <lb n="2"/><w lemma="καλός">καλός</w>
	               </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" n="b">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><add place="overstrike"><orig>αεδ</orig></add>
	               </ab>
                </div>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p><app loc="a.1"><lem><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Φιλ</supplied>ωνί<subst><del rend="corrected">ι</del><add place="overstrike">δ</add></subst>ης</lem>
                <rdg resp="#ferri1922"><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Λε</supplied>ωνίδης</rdg>
                    <rdg resp="#SEG"><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64816"><name><unclear>Λε</unclear>ωνίδης</name></persName></rdg>
                </app>
                </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Phil</supplied>onidès <supplied reason="subaudible">est</supplied> beau!</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Phil</supplied>onides <supplied reason="subaudible">is</supplied> fine!</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Phil</supplied>onides <supplied reason="subaudible">è</supplied> bello!</p>
         </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
                <p>فيلونيديس (يكون) فاضلًا (جيدًا أونبيلًا).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                
               <p>Ferri's drawing and explanation are quite clear: the first letters of the personal name have been later on erased and replaced by three obscure letters (b),
               which is nonsense, thus not translatable. The restoration now proposed, with three letters erased, fits better the space available.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
